<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Flex:opsz,wght@8..144,100..1000&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div>
        <h1 class="display-1">Book Traker</h1>
        <p>The following project allows the user to keep track of the books they have read. The books currently displayed are some of the books that I've read over the years.</p> 
        <form action="/add" method="GET">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btnC">Add a book</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</header>
<main>
    
        <% for(let book of bookList){%>
            <div class="cnt">
                <img src="https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/isbn/<%= book.isbn %>-M.jpg" alt="Book Cover" class="book-cover">
                <div class="bookInfo">
                    <h3><%= book.bookname %></h3>
                    <h5>Author: </h5> <p><%= book.author %></p>
                    <h5>Genre:  </h5> <p><%= book.genre %></p>
                    <h5>ISBN:  </h5> <p><%= book.isbn %></p>
                    <h5>Year Read:</h5> <p><%= book.yearread %> </p>
                    <h5>Rating:  </h5> <p><%= book.rating %></p>
                    <h5>Description:  </h5> <p><%= book.description %></p>
                    <button class="btn btnEd">Edit</button>
                    <button class="btn btnDe">Delete</button>     
                </div>  
            </div>
            <% } %>
    
</main>

<footer>
    
</footer>

</body>
</html>